  <div class="expert"><div class="exp-em">🌍</div><div class="exp-name">R. Dalio</div><div class="exp-style">Macro / All Weather</div><div class="exp-stars">★★★☆☆</div><div style="margin-top:6px;padding:4px 8px;background:var(--yellow-bg);border:1px solid var(--yellow-bdr);border-radius:4px;font-size:9px;color:var(--yellow);text-align:center;font-family:var(--mono);">NEUTRE</div><div class="exp-quote">"Position concentrée risquée macro. Diversifier. Beta 2.38 — trop corrélé aux cycles."</div></div>
